metadata.title: Fat Daddio's Disposable Pastry Bag, 12", 10, Transparent
features: IDEAL FOR A VARIETY OF HOT OR COLD FOODS - Great for filling cupcakes, eclairs, cream puffs or quick frosting color changes
DURABLE POLYETHYLENE MATERIAL - Soft and won't split or slip in your hand
FLEXIBLE - Essential for decorating with ease. Simply cut the end of the bag, drop in the decorating tube of your choice, fill and use. Works with any coupler
description: Fat Daddio's disposable pastry bags help you save time by eliminating clean-up problems. The .0042" Polyethylene material allows these bags to be used with hot or cold food products. The Soft and flexible material ensures Comfort while in use, and prevents slipping in your hand. Simply cut the end of the bag, drop in the decorating tube of your choice, fill and use. Works with any coupler.
